      "is this on your roadmap",
      "does this belong in the roadmap conversation",
      "is this a priority this quarter",
      "or tabled",
      "or table for now",
      "or ignore"
    ],
    "_source": "canon-approved closers (4T transcript + cold-email-archive:646-672)."
  },
